  "body": "Played around with the connection button a bit and saw that we could save a good amount of space without losing clarity by tweaking the icon display. Check it out!\r\n\r\nThis'll help out on denser screens, like transaction history, because we can shrink the entire sidebar along with it.\r\n\r\nDesigns are in the [Dashboard Debugger Figma project](https://www.figma.com/file/SkmEWfaHYjql63yYGWu2Xm/Dashboard-Debugger?type=design&node-id=557%3A1889&t=YRoy4IV4j9GYeErO-1), specifically the Compact Network Button board in the Design System page.\r\n\r\n![Compact Network Button](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/assets/3990373/c588234b-c39d-44f5-9f1f-38d031b9a1cf)",
